{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c3100dad13","title":"复陈毅、邓小平电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66a200b715","index":0,"year":1948,"month":10,"day":28,"articleId":"c3100dad13"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ad133b90c","type":"paragraph","text":"复陈毅、邓小平电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"c3100dad13"},{"id":"3ef39735cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年10月28日）我们同意你们不出准南，但是否打孙元良，要看孙元良是否被你们调动到徐蚌线。如果仍在徐线，则似以不打为宜。你们在徐蚌线以西地区出现，对整个敌人威断极大。这种威励作用，胜过在徐线上打一胜位。请你们考虚到达毫、涡、永中间地区休息数日之后，第一步是否可以分路攻占毫、涡、蒙三城，再看形势。估计三城占领，淮南即将震动，孙、邱两部均将被调动，而你们行动的自的是调动孙、邱，主要是调动邮清泉","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"c3100dad13"}],"page":{"id":"7ca9b6d3f8","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"c3100dad13","start":128,"end":128}}}},"__N_SSG":true}